    <h1>About This Site</h1>
    <p>
        Welcome to Word Game! This site was created to bring you the classic Wordle experience with a fresh green twist. Whether you’re here to challenge yourself daily or just want to have fun guessing words, you’re in the right place.
    </p>
    <p>
        The goal is simple: guess the secret five-letter word in six tries. Every guess helps you get closer with colored clues inspired by the popular game Wordle.
    </p>
    <p>
       Made with fun by Eyal, a coder passionate about clean design and fun challenges. Feel free to reach out if you want to say hi or share your feedback!
    </p>
    <p>
        This project started as a personal challenge to recreate one of my favorite word games, but it quickly grew into a community space for word lovers and puzzle enthusiasts alike. I wanted to keep the game straightforward and addictive, so you can enjoy quick brain workouts anytime.
    </p>
    <p>
        Behind the scenes, the game runs on clean, efficient code with a focus on responsiveness and accessibility. Whether you're playing on a desktop or your phone, Wordle Vibes adapts smoothly to your screen.
    </p>
    <p>
        I’m always looking to improve and add new features, so your suggestions and bug reports are super valuable. Keep an eye out for updates and new twists coming soon!
    </p>
    <p>
        Thanks for stopping by and happy word hunting!
    </p>
